{"about_the_game":"Mech Engineer \u2013 a dark sci-fi mech assembling manager with semi-auto battles against mutating, alien bio-weapon.<br><br>The gameplay is focused on resource management and mech assembly. You almost will not be able to control the Mechs in battle.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429250/extras/assamble_reactor_2.gif?t=1627476136\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>First</strong>. Assemble the heart of the Mech \u2013 <strong>reactor</strong>. Increase its power with components, while keeping temperature down.<br></li><li> Terrain's temperature affects reactors to the point that, it can shut down them.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429250/extras/assamble_weapon_2.gif?t=1627476136\" /><br></li><li><strong>Second</strong>. Then prepare your weapon. Customize rate of fire, weight, energy consumption, accuracy, and firepower.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Different enemies require specific weapons. The rate of fire also changes the speed of spending ammunition.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429250/extras/assamble_mech_2.gif?t=1627476136\" /><br></li><li><strong>Third</strong>. When assembling mechs, the main thing to remember about limiting weight and available energy.<br></li><li> The types of mechs differ from each other also in their adaptability to different terrain.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429250/extras/battle_for_steam_v1.gif?t=1627476136\" /><br></li><li><strong>Fourth</strong>. Sending mechs into battle will provide resources and open up new terrain for completing a global mission.<br></li><li> It is important to control the route on the global map and track the probability of enemy bases on the cells.<br><br><br></li><li><strong>Go